# Public Lab

## 
<!--History & Mission-->

``` A community where you can learn how to investigate environmental concerns. Using inexpensive DIY techniques, we seek to change how people see the world in environmental, social, and political terms.
```

## History

- Mapping in Peru
- Gulf Oil Spill

